<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">萚兮</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson98d78626281f">
<p>萚兮萚兮，风其吹女。叔兮伯兮，倡予和女。<br />萚兮萚兮，风其漂女。叔兮伯兮，倡予要女。</p>
</div>
</div>
